content: Hi, I need some help with my heating system.

Hello! I’m an AI assistant at XYZ home services. It seems you might have reached us by mistake as we handle plumbing, electrical, and HVAC services. Can you please confirm if you are looking to book a service with us?
Oh, actually I think I dialed the wrong number. Sorry about that.
No problem at all! I will mark this as a wrong number so we don’t bother you again. Thank you and have a great day!
